# UI — CaravaggioUI and widget reuse

Read `docs/architecture/WIDGETS_AND_CARAVAGGIO.md` before creating UI.

- Use **CaravaggioUI** (`package:caravaggio_ui/caravaggio_ui.dart`) for buttons, inputs, typography where available.
- Reuse `lib/widgets/common/` widgets before creating new loading/error states.
- Cross-feature reusable components: `lib/features/components/<name>/` with `application/` + `presentation/`.
- Feature-local widgets only: `lib/features/<feature>/presentation/widgets/`.
- Do not duplicate widget policy in comments — follow the architecture doc.
